{"tid":1553124,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【感動】香港反送中運動寫歷史 十大史詩片段鼓舞人心","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:03:21.000Z","uid":113368,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dca31077002de29f454fd680b1807fd588f4d610","tid":1553124,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"我去到獅子山嗰邊已經忍唔到喊左出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇手足可以頂得哂成條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路睇返我地由六月以來所做既一切一切<br />\n<br />\n曾經有好多次想過放棄<br />\n<br />\n現在回想起來<br />\n<br />\n就係好彩我地冇放棄過<br />\n<br />\n一直對抗極權統治政府<br />\n<br />\n先會有現在團結的香港<br />\n<br />\n不是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FtoEwyG9vyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFtoEwyG9vyQ&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=6aedaf33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FtoEwyG9vyQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBetween 強烈要求條片應該新增 加城城買奶粉落十大片段第一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n城城we connected<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143bbf6e84e9dcc8e3def022d7e1ece3c0950651","tid":1553124,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"條條片都喊到我癡線 好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cfff65ca9b413c249aad58290b1f994e812c85","